W5d2
------
In linux moudles are the drivers for kernels
VCAN:
ip link  - interface to configuration
add a device: add dev vcan0 type vcan (this is like the canalyzer device)

man ip link - show manual/help

SocketCAN is like a file, open, write, read , close. To open the com. read and write and the close the com.
To close the socket, since the destructor will do that it contains the close.(according to the example shown in lecture)
Whe socket is open a fd is reacieved.
ioctrl - setting up a can.

